<h1>EV Wraps Chicago &mdash; Tesla, Rivian &amp; Electric Vehicle Specialists</h1>
<p class="lead speakable">Chicago Fleet Wraps is Chicago&rsquo;s premier specialist for electric vehicle wraps. With 24+ years of experience and 9,400+ vehicles wrapped, we understand the unique body panels, frunk geometry, and paint-protection requirements of Tesla, Rivian, Lucid, and other EVs. Zero verified paint damage claims. 2-year workmanship warranty.</p>

<section class="overview">
<h2>Why EV Wraps Require a Specialist</h2>
<p>Electric vehicles present unique challenges that generic wrap shops are not equipped to handle. The large, uninterrupted body panels on a Tesla Model 3 or Rivian R1T require seamless vinyl application without visible seams or stretch marks. The frunk (front trunk) lid, charge port door, and camera housings demand precision cutting and heat-forming techniques that only experienced EV wrap specialists can execute correctly.</p>
<p>Chicago Fleet Wraps has wrapped hundreds of Tesla Model 3, Model Y, Model S, Model X, and Cybertruck vehicles, as well as Rivian R1T and R1S, Lucid Air, and commercial EV fleets. Our certified technicians are trained on EV-specific installation techniques, including proper handling of aluminum body panels and camera/sensor areas.</p>
</section>



